{
  "type": "sectionColumn",
  "id": "immersive_d",
  "width": ["100%", "90%"],
  "height": "hug",
  "align": ["full", "center"],
  "fill": "oklch(from var(--pb-secondary) l c h / 0.33)",
  "borderRadius": ["1.25rem", "2rem"],
  "effects": [
    {
      "type": "backdropBlur",
      "amount": "16px"
    }
  ],
  "marginBottom": ["1.5rem", "3rem"],
  "columns": {
    "mobile": 1,
    "desktop": 4
  },
  "columnWidths": {
    "mobile": [1],
    "desktop": [1, 1, 1, 1]
  },
  "columnGaps": {
    "mobile": "0.75rem",
    "desktop": "0.75rem"
  },
  "columnStyles": {
    "mobile": [
      {
        "padding": "1rem",
        "gap": "0.75rem"
      }
    ],
    "desktop": [
      {
        "padding": "1rem 1.25rem",
        "gap": "0.75rem"
      },
      {
        "padding": "1rem 1.25rem",
        "gap": "0.75rem"
      },
      {
        "padding": "1rem 1.25rem",
        "gap": "0.75rem"
      },
      {
        "padding": "1rem 1.25rem",
        "gap": "0.75rem"
      }
    ]
  },
  "columnSpan": {
    "mobile": {
      "d-label": "all"
    },
    "desktop": {
      "d-label": "all"
    }
  },
  "elementOrder": ["d-label", "d-sensors", "d-software", "d-output", "d-interaction"],
  "definitions": {
    "d-label": {
      "type": "elementHeading",
      "level": 6,
      "text": "TECHNICAL SYSTEM",
      "align": "left",
      "width": "hug",
      "height": "hug",
      "marginBottom": "0.5rem"
    },
    "d-sensors": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Sensing\n\n**Depth** Azure Kinect DK × 6\n\n**Volume** Occupancy 8m × 12m\n\n**Latency** <30ms body-to-render\n\n**Calibration** Auto-corrects on participant entry",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "d-software": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Software\n\n**Runtime** TouchDesigner\n\n**3D Engine** Notch\n\n**Audio** Max/MSP → binaural\n\n**Data pipeline** OSC over LAN, 60Hz tick",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.08
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "d-output": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Output\n\n**Projection** 4 × Christie Laser, 20K lm each\n\n**Resolution** 7680 × 2160 (wrapped)\n\n**Audio** 16-channel ambisonics\n\n**Haptic floor** 8-zone subwoofer array",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.16
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "d-interaction": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Interaction Model\n\n**Trigger zones** 14 spatial thresholds\n\n**Participants** 1–8 simultaneous\n\n**State machine** 6 environment modes\n\n**Session length** ~6 min average",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.24
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "gridMode": {
    "mobile": "columns",
    "desktop": "grid"
  },
  "gridDebug": false,
  "columnAssignments": {
    "mobile": {
      "d-label": 0,
      "d-sensors": 0,
      "d-software": 0,
      "d-output": 0,
      "d-interaction": 0
    },
    "desktop": {
      "d-label": 0,
      "d-sensors": 0,
      "d-software": 1,
      "d-output": 2,
      "d-interaction": 3
    }
  }
}
